OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRather
OL,6,Fcloudy with outbreaks of rain this
OL,7,Fevening, these clearing towards
OL,8,Fmidnight. Then mainly dry through the
OL,9,Fearly hours with long clear spells
OL,10,Fdeveloping and, with northwesterly
OL,11,Fwinds easing, a touch of ground frost
OL,12,Fis possible.
OL,13,
OL,14,CMonday:FAll parts will have a dry day
OL,15,Fwith variable amounts of cloud and
OL,16,Fsome sunny intervals. Mainly light
OL,17,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
