OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FEarly
OL,6,Frain on Tuesday then sunny spells and
OL,7,Fshowers. Rather cold and unsettled
OL,8,FWednesday and Thursday with scattered
OL,9,Fshowers. Chance of overnight frost.
